    JCDiagnostic.MultilineDiagnostic

    public class JCDiagnostic
extends Object
implements Diagnostic<JavaFileObject>
    An abstraction of a diagnostic message generated by the compiler.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

      • JCDiagnostic

        protected JCDiagnostic(DiagnosticFormatter<JCDiagnostic> formatter,
                       JCDiagnostic.DiagnosticInfo diagnosticInfo,
                       Lint.LintCategory lc,
                       Set<JCDiagnostic.DiagnosticFlag> flags,
                       DiagnosticSource source,
                       JCDiagnostic.DiagnosticPosition pos)
        Create a diagnostic object.
        参数:
        formatter - the formatter to use for the diagnostic
        diagnosticInfo - the diagnostic key
        lc - the lint category for the diagnostic
        source - the name of the source file, or null if none.
        pos - the character offset within the source file, if given.
